data.description: Who doesn't want this move in ready gem in the heart of Benson? Renovated in 2021 leaving you with a new roof, retaining wall, hardwood floors, kitchen, bathrooms, plumbing and windows! This 3 bed, 2 bath is walkable to Gallagher park, the Benson strip and Gallagher pool to enjoy the hot summers! Speaking of seasons, go ahead and avoid the brutal winters as much as you can with your 1 car attached garage! No dusting snow off their car every winter for this homeowner! The stainless steel kitchen appliances leave your newly renovated kitchen feeling complete. The only home in this area with so much to offer!
